Package com.igrium.videolib.api.playback

Interface VideoEvents

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseVideoEvents, VLCEvents
public interface VideoEvents
An interface for registering and un-registering callbacks pertaining to video playback. All callbacks will be triggered on the Minecraft client thread.
